Obs.: Ponte Preta and Bandeirante, relegated in 1987 from 2nd Level, won the
right to play in the 1st Level. In a boycott against this decision, all the
other teams, except Corinthians, refused to play against them and were
considered losers by WO. The only realized matches were:
20/Mar Ponte Preta 5-1 Bandeirante
21/Apr Corinthians 0-0 Ponte Preta
